OL,3,CWest Brom fined #30,000 over crowd
OL,4,Ctrouble at Wolves FA Cup game
OL,6,FWest Brom have been fined #30,000 and
OL,7,Fgiven a warning over the crowd trouble
OL,8,Fwhich marred their FA Cup fixture
OL,9,Fagainst local rivals Wolves in January.
OL,11,FA Wolves fan celebrating a goal while
OL,12,Fin a home section of the Hawthorns
OL,13,Fsparked the worst of the disorder in
OL,14,Fthe 79th minute, forcing the game to
OL,15,Fbe suspended for 38 minutes.
OL,17,FWest Brom admitted two Football
OL,18,FAssociation charges concerning the
OL,19,Fbehaviour of their supporters and the
OL,20,Fthrowing of missiles towards the pitch.
