OL,6,FAn independent regulatory commission
OL,7,Fgave the club credit for that early
OL,8,Fplea and for making "genuine and
OL,9,Fconcerted" efforts to comply with FA
OL,10,Frules on crowd conduct.
OL,12,FHowever, the panel felt they "fell
OL,13,Fshort" in a number of areas which were
OL,14,F"significant and serious".
