OL,3,CWest Brom fined #30,000 over crowd
OL,4,Ctrouble at Wolves FA Cup game
OL,6,FWest Brom managing director Mark Miles
OL,7,Fsaid: "While the written reasons state
OL,8,Fthe club did a very considerable
OL,9,Fnumber of things right and plainly
OL,10,Ftook its responsibilities seriously,
OL,11,Fit is clear there were also areas in
OL,12,Fwhich we fell short, and it is
OL,13,Fimperative we continue to focus on
OL,14,Fthese aspects as we strive for
OL,15,Fimprovement."
