OL,3,CWest Brom fined #30,000 over crowd
OL,4,Ctrouble at Wolves FA Cup game
OL,6,F"Since the fixture, the club has met
OL,7,Fwith the Sports Ground Safety
OL,8,FAuthority, acting on its
OL,9,Frecommendations to improve internal
OL,10,Fprocedures which will help to prevent
OL,11,Fsimilar issues arising in the future."
OL,13,F"The behaviour we witnessed that day
OL,14,Fis totally unacceptable, and the club
OL,15,Fhas since banned or suspended in
OL,16,Fexcess of 40 supporters who were
OL,17,Finvolved in the incident. West
OL,18,FMidlands Police is also continuing its
OL,19,Fown criminal investigations into
OL,20,Findividual fan behaviour."
